r radiation from dust by relativistic electrons may\ncontribute substantially to the large-scale diffuse TeV emission observed\ntowards the central regions of the Galaxy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Aug 2006 17:49:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Nov 2006 14:27:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
