 that this state also shows strongly enhanced dimer\ncorrelations, in qualitative accord with the large-N results. We compare our\nresults with a recent QMC study of the SU(4) Heisenberg model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Aug 2006 19:05:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 29 Apr 2007 14:48:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
