e understanding\nof the structure and molecular dynamics of C60 superconductors, these results\nmay help in clarifying the effects of the structure on the superconducting\nproperties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Aug 2006 18:09:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 29 Sep 2006 17:06:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
